{"title":"Java学习-自定义简单函数","date":"2018-03-11T07:17:06.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 11, 2018","L":"03/11/2018","MM-DD":"03-11"},"link":"2018/03/11/Learning-20180311Java学习-自定义简单函数","comments":true,"tags":["Java"],"categories":["Learning"],"updated":"2021-02-18T03:38:14.387Z","content":"<p><strong>自定义简单函数</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>学习编写静态(static)函数、函数的参数、返回值的使用, 函数的具体实现。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/*输入双精度数字函数*/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">double</span> <span class=\"title\">inputNumber</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    Scanner scanner = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Scanner(System.in);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">double</span> number =  scanner.nextDouble();</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> number;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>注</strong>：系统的输入，需要在主类前导入扫描类包，即在主类前添加一下代码：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> java.util.Scanner;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>笔记：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>static是定义静态函数的意思；</li>\n<li>inputNumber是函数名，前面的double指此函数的返回类型，还可以是其他的如：int,Int,Double,void等；</li>\n<li>scanner是实例化的扫描类；</li>\n<li>函数返回类型不是void的就要添加语句return进行值返回，此例返回输入的双精度变量number的值；</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">static</span> Double <span class=\"title\">Calculate</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">double</span> x,<span class=\"keyword\">char</span> c,<span class=\"keyword\">double</span> y)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(c==<span class=\"string\">&#x27;+&#x27;</span>)<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> x+y;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(c==<span class=\"string\">&#x27;-&#x27;</span>)<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> x-y;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(c==<span class=\"string\">&#x27;*&#x27;</span>)<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> x*y;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(c==<span class=\"string\">&#x27;/&#x27;</span>)<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> x/y;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>笔记：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>函数后面需要添加一对小括号，用来接收参数供函数处理，可以接收多个参数，在里面定义的参数叫形参；</li>\n<li>if-else是选择语句,表示如果（条件是真的）就{执行代码}，否者执行{}；</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>主函数调用自定义函数</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">(String\\[\\] args)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">&quot;--------简单计算器-------&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    Scanner scanner = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Scanner(System.in);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">true</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        System.out.print(<span class=\"string\">&quot;请输入第一个数：&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">double</span> x = inputNumber();              <span class=\"comment\">//inputNumber函数调用</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        System.out.print(<span class=\"string\">&quot;请输入运算符号：&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        String cc = scanner.next();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">char</span> c = cc.charAt(<span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        System.out.print(<span class=\"string\">&quot;请输入第二个数：&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">double</span> y = inputNumber();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        System.out.print(<span class=\"string\">&quot;运算结果：&quot;</span> + Calculate(x,c,y));    <span class=\"comment\">// Calculate函数调用</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">&quot;\\\\n-------\\\\n还需要继续吗？Y（yes）/N(no)：&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        cc = scanner.next();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(cc.equals(<span class=\"string\">&quot;N&quot;</span>)||cc.equals(<span class=\"string\">&quot;n&quot;</span>)||cc.equals(<span class=\"string\">&quot;no&quot;</span>)||cc.equals(<span class=\"string\">&quot;NO&quot;</span>)||cc.equals(<span class=\"string\">&quot;No&quot;</span>))<span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">     &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">     System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">&quot;---------------------\\\\nBye!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>笔记：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>由于Java Scanner没有nextChar()的输入，但可以通过 String cc = scanner.next(); char c = cc.charAt(0); 接收到cc字符串，取cc其中一个为char c；</li>\n<li>while(true)执行死循环；</li>\n<li>||表示或者的意思。例子中输入N或n或no或NO或No就可以退出循环；</li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"Java学习-值类型的变量和值及其运算","link":"2018/03/13/Learning-20180313Java学习-值类型的变量和值及其运算"},"next":{"title":"Java学习-Java基本输入输出","link":"2018/03/11/Learning-20180311Java学习-Java基本输入输出"},"plink":"https://www.zzboy.cn/2018/03/11/Learning-20180311Java学习-自定义简单函数/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Patrick Jun","link":"<a href=\"https://www.zzboy.cn/2018/03/11/Learning-20180311Java学习-自定义简单函数/\" title=\"Java学习-自定义简单函数\">https://www.zzboy.cn/2018/03/11/Learning-20180311Java学习-自定义简单函数/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"March 11, 2018"}}